snippet.title: Amber Heard on Her Bisexuality and "Salacious" Johnny Depp Romance
snippet.description:
Engaged couple Johnny Depp and Amber Heard aren't quite wrapped up in wedding planning just yet. The celebrity duo is making headlines for some exciting upcoming projects, including how Johnny is reportedly in talks to play famous escape artist Harry Houdini. On the other hand, his ladylove opened up in the latest issue of W about her previous relationship with photographer Tasya van Ree. Check out the video to get the full story!
